# Azure DevOps Work Item Integration

## Tool Locations

| Tool | Path | Purpose |
|------|------|---------|
| PAT Manager | `DevTools/AzureTools/Azure-DevOpsPAT-Manager/` | Personal Access Token setup |
| Work Item Manager | `DevTools/AzureTools/Azure-DevOpsUserStoryManager/` | Single work item CRUD |
| Bulk Creator | `DevTools/AzureTools/Azure-DevOpsItemCreator/` | Hierarchical bulk creation from JSON |
| Story Tracker | `DevTools/AzureTools/Azure-StoryTracker/` | Helper scripts for `/azstory` command |

## Available Actions (Azure-DevOpsUserStoryManager)

| Action | Purpose | Required Parameters |
|--------|---------|---------------------|
| `Get` | Retrieve work item details | `-WorkItemId` |
| `Update` | Modify work item description | `-WorkItemId`, `-Description` |
| `Comment` | Add discussion comment | `-WorkItemId`, `-Comment` |
| `Attach` | Upload file attachment | `-WorkItemId`, `-FilePath` |
| `Link` | Add repository link or hyperlink | `-WorkItemId`, `-Url`, `-Title` |
| `Status` | Change work item state | `-WorkItemId`, `-State` |
| `Subtask` | Create child item (Task or Bug) | `-WorkItemId`, `-Title`, `-Description`, `-Type` |
| `AddTags` | Add tags to work item | `-WorkItemId`, `-Tags` (semicolon-separated) |

## State Transitions

```
New -> Active          (when starting work)
Active -> Resolved     (work complete, pending review)
Resolved -> Closed     (reviewed and approved)
Active -> Closed       (work cancelled or rejected)
Any -> Removed         (if cancelled)
```

## Language Standards

- **Titles and descriptions** for new work items: Use **Norwegian** (Bokmal)
- **Comments**: Can be English or Norwegian, prefer Norwegian for consistency
- **Tags**: Use English for technical tags (e.g., `BugFix`, `Tested`, `ReadyForReview`, `AzStory`)

